<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 18:08:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>与警方的说法相矛盾，在被以色列士兵杀害的男子尸体中发现子弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/contradicting-police-claim-bullet-found-in-body-of-man-killed-by-israeli-soldier/0000018c-5460-df2f-adac-fe6d2d720000</link><description>以色列士兵阿维亚德·弗里贾 (Aviad Frija) 在一次枪击袭击中多次向尤瓦尔·凯斯特尔曼开枪，声称他认为自己是恐怖分子。警方表示不需要尸检后，他的尸体被埋葬，宪兵队得出相反结论后，他的尸体被挖掘出来</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 17:27:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/contradicting-police-claim-bullet-found-in-body-of-man-killed-by-israeli-soldier/0000018c-5460-df2f-adac-fe6d2d720000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡抨击普京俄罗斯的“反以色列”立场和伊朗关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/netanyahu-slams-putin-for-russias-anti-israel-stance-iran-ties/0000018c-53e5-d6bd-a1ad-7bf7f45e0000</link><description>克里姆林宫去年 10 月接待了哈马斯官员代表团，此后一直保持与伊朗的联系，克里姆林宫表示，这次 50 分钟的通话主要围绕加沙的人道主义危机</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 15:34:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/netanyahu-slams-putin-for-russias-anti-israel-stance-iran-ties/0000018c-53e5-d6bd-a1ad-7bf7f45e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军透露，自 10 月 7 日以来，已有 1,593 名以色列士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/1-593-israeli-soldiers-wounded-since-october-7-idf-reveals/0000018c-5416-df2f-adac-fe3fbe6d0000</link><description>与过去的冲突和战争不同，以色列军队隐瞒了受伤士兵及其状况的报告。在《国土报》报道称军方拒绝这样做后，军方才公布了这一信息</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 15:22:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/1-593-israeli-soldiers-wounded-since-october-7-idf-reveals/0000018c-5416-df2f-adac-fe3fbe6d0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙最古老的清真寺之一在战斗中受损；以色列国防军称，它被哈马斯使用</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/one-of-gazas-oldest-mosques-damaged-in-fighting-it-was-used-by-hamas-idf-says/0000018c-53d7-db23-ad9f-7bdf62f30000</link><description>视频显示，这座清真寺被认为是加沙地带最重要的历史建筑之一，但其地基已被摧毁，内部大厅已被完全摧毁。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 14:38:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/one-of-gazas-oldest-mosques-damaged-in-fighting-it-was-used-by-hamas-idf-says/0000018c-53d7-db23-ad9f-7bdf62f30000</guid></item><item><title>十字军在圣地吃什么？考古学家亲自动手寻找答案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-12-10/ty-article-magazine/what-did-crusaders-eat-in-the-holy-land-archaeologists-get-hands-dirty-to-find-out/0000018c-536f-df2f-adac-ff6f59280000</link><description>以色列的新研究揭示了十字军在繁荣时期的消费情况，以及在马穆鲁克人将十字军困在阿波罗尼亚城堡中的围困期间的消费情况</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 12:23:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-12-10/ty-article-magazine/what-did-crusaders-eat-in-the-holy-land-archaeologists-get-hands-dirty-to-find-out/0000018c-536f-df2f-adac-ff6f59280000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡必须在政治上被摧毁，否则以色列将与他一起灭亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-must-be-politically-destroyed-or-israel-will-go-down-with-him/0000018c-530f-db23-ad9f-7bdfeca10000</link><description>关于总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的最大神话之一是他是一位精明的政治家。他对伊朗、美国、哈马斯和其他关键领域的外交政策表明恰恰相反</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 11:01:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-must-be-politically-destroyed-or-israel-will-go-down-with-him/0000018c-530f-db23-ad9f-7bdfeca10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列称摩萨德帮助挫败了伊朗在塞浦路斯的恐怖阴谋</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/two-iranians-questioned-over-suspected-plots-to-attack-israelis-in-cyprus/0000018c-5349-db23-ad9f-7bd9a8230000</link><description>据当地媒体报道，据信这两人正处于收集有关以色列潜在目标情报的早期阶段。塞浦路斯是成千上万以色列人的热门度假和投资目的地</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 11:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/two-iranians-questioned-over-suspected-plots-to-attack-israelis-in-cyprus/0000018c-5349-db23-ad9f-7bd9a8230000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装对以色列船只的威胁可能导致红海全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/houthi-threats-against-israel-bound-ships-could-lead-to-war-in-the-red-sea/0000018c-5124-df2f-adac-ff2d1f120000</link><description>胡塞武装警告说，任何前往以色列的船只都是目标，这可能会使红海成为新的军事对抗的焦点。可能需要的是在不久的将来展示武力，这也将对抗伊朗持续的威胁</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 07:29:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/.premium/houthi-threats-against-israel-bound-ships-could-lead-to-war-in-the-red-sea/0000018c-5124-df2f-adac-ff2d1f120000</guid></item><item><title>安全消息人士称，以色列军队无法为哈马斯的另一项释放人质协议创造条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article-live/israels-ground-offensive-in-gaza-deepens-as-arab-eu-leaders-push-for-a-cease-fire/0000018c-5187-df2f-adac-ffaf03700000</link><description>随着越来越多的国家呼吁立即停火，以色列国防军在加沙的地面行动仍在进行中 ■ 美国在否决联合国安理会停火决议一天后跳过国会审查批准向以色列出售坦克炮弹 ■ 也门胡塞武装表示一切红海中前往以色列的船只被视为目标 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列境内至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生；超过 138 名人质仍被扣押在加沙 ■ 哈马斯卫生部声称 17,700 人死亡，48,700 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 06:35:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article-live/israels-ground-offensive-in-gaza-deepens-as-arab-eu-leaders-push-for-a-cease-fire/0000018c-5187-df2f-adac-ffaf03700000</guid></item><item><title>以色列打击加沙哈马斯的时间已所剩无几，美国的耐心已所剩无几</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/streching-u-s-patience-time-is-running-out-on-israels-campaign-against-hamas-in-gaza/0000018c-506d-df4b-a78e-d16f72cf0000</link><description>美国否决了联合国安理会的停火要求，并提出向以色列提供 45,000 枚坦克炮弹的协议，但白宫对以色列的支持并非无限</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Dec 2023 04:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-10/ty-article/streching-u-s-patience-time-is-running-out-on-israels-campaign-against-hamas-in-gaza/0000018c-506d-df4b-a78e-d16f72cf0000</guid></item><item><title>两名阿拉伯裔以色列兄弟在以色列北部城市海法涉嫌双重凶杀案中被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/two-arab-israeli-brothers-shot-dead-in-suspected-double-homicide-in-haifa/0000018c-505f-df4b-a78e-d15fc18e0000</link><description>萨米尔·赛义德 (Samir Said) 和萨梅赫·赛义德 (Sameh Said) 两兄弟在城市停车场被红大卫盾会医护人员发现，情况危急，随后被宣布当场死亡</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 21:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/two-arab-israeli-brothers-shot-dead-in-suspected-double-homicide-in-haifa/0000018c-505f-df4b-a78e-d15fc18e0000</guid></item><item><title>四名以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生； 10 月 7 日，一名士兵因受伤死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/four-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting-soldier-dies-of-wounds-inflicted-on-oct-7/0000018c-4fa4-df4b-a78e-dfa7483c0000</link><description>阵亡士兵中包括以色列战时内阁成员加迪·艾森科特的侄子，他在加沙地带南部的战斗中阵亡两天前失去了自己的儿子</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 20:13:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/four-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting-soldier-dies-of-wounds-inflicted-on-oct-7/0000018c-4fa4-df4b-a78e-dfa7483c0000</guid></item><item><title>“每一天都是地狱，这让我想起大屠杀”：获释人质回忆哈马斯被囚禁的时光</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/it-reminded-me-of-the-holocaust-freed-hostages-recount-time-in-captivity/0000018c-4fd1-df4b-a78e-dfd3e0cf0000</link><description>在特拉维夫的一次集会上，播放了从哈马斯囚禁中释放的以色列人讲述他们被关押条件的视频证词。 “我以为我疯了，”其中一人说道，“我孤身一人，几乎没有光，也几乎没有食物。那里的一天就像一整周”</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 19:23:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/it-reminded-me-of-the-holocaust-freed-hostages-recount-time-in-captivity/0000018c-4fd1-df4b-a78e-dfd3e0cf0000</guid></item><item><title>也门胡塞武装称他们将袭击红海前往以色列的船只</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/yemens-houthis-say-they-will-target-ships-in-red-sea-en-route-to-israel/0000018c-4fa4-df2f-adac-ffad39350000</link><description>伊朗支持的也门代理部队一直在向以色列发射导弹和无人机，并瞄准与以色列有联系的船只。一名以色列国防官员告诉《纽约时报》，如果有任何导弹或无人机成功抵达以色列，以色列很难不做出回应</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 19:19:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/yemens-houthis-say-they-will-target-ships-in-red-sea-en-route-to-israel/0000018c-4fa4-df2f-adac-ffad39350000</guid></item><item><title>拜登自加沙地面行动开始以来首次投出否决权；以色列不确定他会重蹈覆辙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/biden-casts-first-veto-since-war-began-israel-isnt-sure-hell-repeat-this/0000018c-4fa1-db23-ad9f-6ff90d220000</link><description>以色列战时内阁成员近日获悉，拜登政府内部在继续全力支持以色列方面遇到了越来越大的困难，这既是出于内部政治考虑，也是因为人们认为几个阿拉伯国家对战争的默默支持正在减弱。</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 18:51:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/biden-casts-first-veto-since-war-began-israel-isnt-sure-hell-repeat-this/0000018c-4fa1-db23-ad9f-6ff90d220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外交部长否认为内塔尼亚胡的儿子亚伊尔和党员订购外交护照</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-minister-denies-ordering-diplomatic-passports-for-netanyahus-son/0000018c-4f53-d6bd-a1ad-7fd75cb10000</link><description>外交部长埃利·科恩拒绝了《国土报》关于他下令向有影响力的利库德集团成员发放外交护照的报道，但外交部长明确表示他正在听从科恩的命令</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 18:15:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-foreign-minister-denies-ordering-diplomatic-passports-for-netanyahus-son/0000018c-4f53-d6bd-a1ad-7fd75cb10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部阿拉伯小镇男子因涉嫌刑事争斗被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-arab-town-in-northern-israel-in-suspected-criminal-feud/0000018c-4f28-df2f-adac-ff2dd95f0000</link><description>这起涉嫌谋杀案发生之际，自 10 月 7 日加沙战争爆发以来，以色列阿拉伯社区的犯罪率有所下降</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 15:47:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-dead-in-arab-town-in-northern-israel-in-suspected-criminal-feud/0000018c-4f28-df2f-adac-ff2dd95f0000</guid></item><item><title>战争期间，六名巴勒斯坦人死在以色列监狱中，其中两人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/six-palestinians-have-died-in-israeli-prisons-during-the-war-two-found-bruised/0000018c-4ea8-df4b-a78e-dfab60f10000</link><description>证据显示，在以色列议会决定恶化巴勒斯坦囚犯的条件的背景下，至少有两名死者遭受了暴力。一个人权组织称，“负责监狱服务的部长鼓励报复行为”</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 15:26:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/six-palestinians-have-died-in-israeli-prisons-during-the-war-two-found-bruised/0000018c-4ea8-df4b-a78e-dfab60f10000</guid></item><item><title>25 岁的萨哈尔·巴鲁克 (Sahar Baruch) 从贝埃里基布兹 (Kibbutz Be&amp;#39;eri) 被劫持到加沙，在囚禁中被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/sahar-baruch-25-taken-hostage-to-gaza-from-kibbutz-beeri-killed-in-captivity/0000018c-4e5d-db23-ad9f-6edde6c60000</link><description>巴鲁克在被劫持为人质之前，一直和他的兄弟躲在加沙边境附近的家中。他的兄弟和祖母被谋杀</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 13:33:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/sahar-baruch-25-taken-hostage-to-gaza-from-kibbutz-beeri-killed-in-captivity/0000018c-4e5d-db23-ad9f-6edde6c60000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦卫生部称周五以色列军队在西岸开火造成六人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-health-ministry-says-six-killed-by-israeli-army-fire-in-west-bank/0000018c-4e28-df2f-adac-fe2dd4670000</link><description>这六人在与以色列军队的交火中丧生，当时以色列军队正在法拉难民营执行逮捕通缉犯的军事行动。其中两人是军方已知的通缉犯</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 11:30:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-09/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-health-ministry-says-six-killed-by-israeli-army-fire-in-west-bank/0000018c-4e28-df2f-adac-fe2dd4670000</guid></item></channel></rss>